<br />\n與中山大學 以及何君堯律師嗰間Anglia Ruskin同級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cc5ce27e0616b3a7d3eb3d98d0264e3a9306a8d","tid":1078786,"uid":82938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T15:32:38.000Z","msg":"滕錦光生於浙江省溫州市，在內地完成本科後赴澳洲攻讀博士。他1994年起在理大任職，在2006至2010年出任協理副校長，2005年起成為結構工程講座教授至今。去年4月，他被深圳南方科技大學「挖角」，他在該校出任副校長兼研究生院院長。<br />\n去年南科大挖角 任內爆基因嬰風波<br />\n南方科技大學在英國《泰晤士高等教育》「世界大學排名2019」位列第301至350名；理大在同一排名榜位列159名。南科大副教授賀建奎因早前宣稱經胚胎基因編輯，令孿生女嬰對愛滋病免疫，惹起全球爭議，南科大當時曾發表聲明，稱賀建奎的研究嚴重違背學術倫理和學術規範，會成立獨立委員會調查。<br />\n滕錦光在南科大做副校長期間，理大有保留其職銜。據理大網頁資料，滕目前是「高讚明可持續結構及材料教授及結構工程講座教授」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n只係poly前教授<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53a143582d25671fcdfe3b41e1f186a37cdb4b5e","tid":1078786,"uid":56624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T16:00:25.000Z","msg":"擁抱大灣區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e57c55439538e6b19a63a6ffb84892cdb301ca26","tid":1078786,"uid":113183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T16:05:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DRXjrhZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDRXjrhZ.png&h=400d3d4f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4572f9fc560c23522c89ad804c786d7a3b343aea","tid":1078786,"uid":29093,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T16:07:00.000Z","msg":"LI GONG U <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9422fde0f9aa1e6d3b092910051bb0ea67e2f7de","tid":1078786,"uid":82938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e57c55439538e6b19a63a6ffb84892cdb301ca26","tid":1078786,"uid":113183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T16:05:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https